<topic id="topic_nkc_bcg_pcb">
    <title>Shared topic inheriting scoped-key values</title>
    <body>
        <p>This topic appears without modification under three branches of the root map. </p>
        <section id="section_nsq_qhs_pcb">
            <title>Keywords</title>
            <p>The following keywords should inherit their values from a keyscope defined in a
                parent topic or map. </p>
            <p><codeph>&lt;keyword keyref="k_kw_server-name"/&gt;</codeph> should produce <keyword
                    keyref="k_kw_server-name"/></p>
            <p><codeph>&lt;keyword keyref="k_kw_platform-name"/&gt;</codeph> should produce <keyword
                    keyref="k_kw_platform-name"/></p>
        </section>
    </body>
</topic>
